ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Authorizing Canadians to accept and wear the Non-Article 5 North Atlantic Treaty Organization Medal for Service in relation to Operation "Sea Guardian"
PrecisOrder (1) authorizing Canadians to accept and wear the NON-ARTICLE 5 NORTH ATLANTIC TREATY ORGANIZATION (NATO) MEDAL FOR SERVICE with NATO in relation to Operation ʺ SEA GUARDIANʺ in recognition of honourable service (2) directs that the Medal follow the Non-Article 5 NATO Medal for service on operation ʺ UNIFIED PROTECTOR - LIBYA
